com.linecorp.armeria.server.docs

Interface TypeInfo

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClassInfo, CollectionInfo
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    EnumInfo, ExceptionInfo, ListInfo, MapInfo, SetInfo, StructInfo, UnresolvedClassInfo

    public interface TypeInfo
    Metadata about the type of a field or a return value.

      • signature

        java.lang.String signature()
        Returns the type signature string of a field or a return value. For example:
        • STRING (base types)
        • LIST<com.linecorp.bar.BarStruct> (containers)
        • com.linecorp.foo.FooStruct (structs and enums)
